						               													<description>Every day on the Frontier is an adventure. Especially in the region around the ruins of Brimstone. As Rolling Tumbleweed blows across the trails and the Crisp Morning Air settles into the streets, you never know what new excitement the day will bring. Will a Derailed Train tear through the town, a Fire spread through the Camp, or is Luck in the Air? There may even be a Killer on the Loose. Yes, life is always exciting in the shadows of Brimstone. Short...but exciting.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 15 card Game Supplement for the Shadows of Brimstone Frontier Town Expansion includes a brand new set of Frontier Town Daily Event cards to liven up your Town Stays. These cards can be added to the Frontier Daily Event deck to nearly double the number of cards, adding fantastic variety to your Town Stays between every Adventure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher's website&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
